\c 6
\s USolomoni wakha ithempeli
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wamakhulu amane lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili emva kokuphuma kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni leGibhithe\x + 2 Lan. 3.1,2.\x*, ngomnyaka wesine wokubusa kukaSolomoni koIsrayeli\x + 2 Lan. 3.2.\x*, ngenyanga kaZivi, eyinyanga yesibili, \add waqala\add* ukwakha indlu yeN\nd kosi\x + Nani 1.1.\x*\nd*.
\v 2 Njalo indlu inkosi uSolomoni eyayakhela uJehova, ubude bayo babuzingalo ezingamatshumi ayisithupha, lobubanzi bayo babungamatshumi amabili, lokuphakama kwayo kwakuzingalo ezingamatshumi amathathu\x + 2 Lan. 3.3,4. Hez. 40. 41. 42.\x*.
\v 3 Lekhulusi phambi kwethempeli lendlu, ubude balo babuzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili, njengobubanzi bendlu, ububanzi balo babuzingalo ezilitshumi phambi kwendlu.
\v 4 Njalo wayenzela indlu amawindi abanzi ngaphandle kulangaphakathi.
\p
\v 5 Futhi emdulini wendlu wakha amakamelo inhlangothi zonke, imiduli yendlu inhlangothi zonke, esenzela ithempeli lendawo yelizwi\x + 6.16,19,20,21,23,31. 7.49. 8.6,8. 2 Lan. 3.16. 4.20. 5.7,9. Hlab. 28.2.\x*. Wenza lezindlwana eziseceleni inhlangothi zonke.
\v 6 Ikamelo elingaphansi kwawo wonke, ububanzi balo babuzingalo ezinhlanu, leliphakathi, ububanzi balo buzingalo eziyisithupha, lelesithathu, ububanzi balo buzingalo eziyisikhombisa. Ngoba ngaphandle kwendlu wenza izinciphiso inhlangothi zonke, ukuze \add imijabo\add* ingagxunyekwa emidulini yendlu\x + Hez. 41.6.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo indlu, isakhiwa, yakhiwa ngamatshe ayepheleliswe enkwalini, ukuze kungezwakali isando lehloka, loba yisiphi isikhali sensimbi endlini nxa isakhiwa\x + 5.18. Dute. 27.5,6.\x*.
\v 8 Umnyango wendlwana eseceleni ephakathi wawusehlangothini lwesokunene lwendlu; njalo bakhwela ngesikhwelo esibhodayo ukuya kwengaphakathi, lokusuka kwengaphakathi kusiya kweyesithathu.
\v 9 Wayakha-ke indlu, wayiqeda; wagubuzela indlu ngentungo lamapulanka emisedari\x + 6.14,38.\x*.
\v 10 Wasesakha izindlwana eceleni kwendlu yonke, ubude bazo buzingalo ezinhlanu, wakuxhuma endlini ngezigodo zemisedari.
\p
\v 11 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuSolomoni lathi:
\v 12 \add Mayelana la\add*le indlu oyakhayo, uba uhamba ngezimiso zami, usenza izahlulelo zami, njalo ugcina yonke imilayo yami ukuhamba ngayo\x + 9.4. 2.4.\x*, ngizakwenza ilizwi lami kuwe engalikhuluma kuDavida uyihlo\x + 2 Sam. 7.13. 1 Lan. 22.10.\x*;
\v 13 ngizahlala phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 25.8. Levi 26.11.\x*, ngingabatshiyi abantu bami uIsrayeli\x + Dute. 31.6,8. Josh. 1.5.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Wayakha-ke uSolomoni indlu, wayiqeda\x + 6.9,38.\x*.
\v 15 Wasesakha imiduli yendlu ngaphakathi ngamapulanka emisedari, kusukela kuphansi lendlu kuze kufike emidulini yophahla\x + 6.16,30.7.7. Nani 5.17.\x*, wayembesa ngaphakathi ngezigodo, wendlala iphansi lendlu ngamapulanka amafiri\x + 5.8.\x*.
\v 16 Wasesakha izingalo ezingamatshumi amabili emaceleni endlu, ngamapulanka emisedari, kusukela kuphansi kwaze kwafika emidulini; wayakhela ngaphakathi, esenzela indawo yelizwi, esenzela ingcwele yezingcwele\x + 7.50. 8.6. Eks. 26.33. 2 Lan. 3.8,10. Hez. 45.3. Heb. 9.3.\x*.
\v 17 Lendlu, elithempeli, ngaphambili, yayizingalo ezingamatshumi amane.
\v 18 Njalo umsedari wendlu ngaphakathi wawubazwe waba zinduku lamaluba avulekileyo; konke kwakungumsedari, kungabonakali litshe.
\v 19 Waselungisa indawo yelizwi phakathi endlini ukubeka khona umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 20 Lendawo yelizwi ephambili, ubude babuzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili, lobubanzi buzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili, lokuphakama kwayo kuzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili; wayihuqa ngegolide elicwengekileyo; wasesembesa ilathi \add ngo\add*msedari.
\v 21 USolomoni waseyihuqa indlu ngaphakathi ngegolide elicwengekileyo, wenza isehlukaniso ngamaketane egolide phambi kwendawo yelizwi, wasesihuqa ngegolide.
\v 22 Lendlu yonke wayihuqa ngegolide yaze yaphelela yonke indlu; lelathi lonke elisendaweni yelizwi walihuqa ngegolide\x + Eks. 30.1,3,6.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Endaweni yelizwi wasesenza \w amakherubhi\w** amabili ngesihlahla somhlwathi\x + Eks. 37.7-9. 2 Lan. 3.10-13.\x*, ukuphakama kwakuzingalo ezilitshumi ngalinye.
\v 24 Olunye uphiko lwekherubhi lwaluzingalo ezinhlanu, lolunye uphiko lwekherubhi lwaluzingalo ezinhlanu; kusukela ekucineni ko\add lunye\add* uphiko kusiya ekucineni ko\add lunye\add* uphiko kwakuzingalo ezilitshumi.
\v 25 Lelinye ikherubhi lalizingalo ezilitshumi; womabili amakherubhi ayeyisilinganiso sinye lesimo sinye.
\v 26 Ukuphakama kwelinye ikherubhi kwakuzingalo ezilitshumi, lelinye ikherubhi lalinjalo.
\v 27 Wasewabeka amakherubhi phakathi kwendlu engaphakathi; njalo amakherubhi elula impiko, kuze kuthi olunye uphiko lwathinta umduli, lophiko lwelinye ikherubhi lwathinta omunye umduli, lempiko zawo zathintana uphiko lophiko ngaphakathi kwendlu\x + Eks. 25.20. 37.9. 2 Lan. 5.8.\x*.
\v 28 Wasewahuqa amakherubhi ngegolide.
\v 29 Wabaza imiduli yonke yendlu inhlangothi zonke ngemifanekiso ebaziweyo yamakherubhi lezihlahla zamalala lamaluba avulekileyo ngaphakathi langaphandle.
\v 30 Iphansi lendlu waselihuqa ngegolide ngaphakathi langaphandle.
\p
\v 31 Emnyango wendawo yelizwi wenza izivalo zesihlahla somhlwathi, ikhothamo \add le\add*migubazi kulezinhlangothi ezinhlanu.
\v 32 Lezivalo zombili zazingezesihlahla somhlwathi, wabaza kuzo imibazo yamakherubhi lezihlahla zamalala lamaluba avulekileyo, wazihuqa ngegolide, wakhandela igolide phezu kwamakherubhi lezihlahla zamalala.
\v 33 Ngokunjalo wasesenzela umnyango wethempeli imigubazi yesihlahla somhlwathi, ezinhlangothini ezine.
\v 34 Lezivalo ezimbili zazingezezihlahla zamafiri\x + 5.8.\x*; impiko zombili zesivalo esisodwa zazigoqeka, lezilenge ezimbili zesivalo sesibili zazigoqeka\x + Hez. 41.24.\x*.
\v 35 Wasebaza \add kuzo\add* amakherubhi lezihlahla zamalala lamaluba avulekileyo, wakuhuqa ngegolide elendlala kuhle phezu kokubaziweyo.
\p
\v 36 Wasesakha iguma elingaphakathi ngemizila emithathu yamatshe abaziweyo, lomzila wemijabo yemisedari\x + 7.12.\x*.
\p
\v 37 Ngomnyaka wesine isisekelo sendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* sabekwa, ngenyanga kaZivi.
\v 38 Kwathi ngomnyaka wetshumi lanye, enyangeni kaBuli, okuyinyanga yesificaminwembili, yaphela indlu ezintweni zayo zonke lanjengakho konke ukumiswa kwayo. Ngakho wayakha iminyaka eyisikhombisa\x + 6.1.\x*.
